#Selection challenge 09 (GCSECS.com)
#Remember BIDMAS from maths?
#Brackets can influence the flow
#To get into a club you must be over 18, but...
#...you can either have an invite or be a member
#Code this algorithm
print("Hey, im the bouncer, welcome to the club!")
age = int(input("How old are you!"))
member = str(input("Are you a member(yes or no)"))
invite = str(input("Did you get an invite?"))

if age > 18 or member == "yes" or invite == "yes" :
  print("Welcome!")
else:
  print("Nu Uh!")
